branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series CVM3 is a valve mounted cylinder with single acting, spring return or spring extend actuation. CVM3 has eight mounting options available and bore sizes range from 20mm to 40mm. A cylinder with the auto switch installed can also be manufactured.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;UL&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Single acting, spring return/extend, valve mounted&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Applicable bores (mm): 20, 25, 32, 40&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Standard strokes (mm): 25, 50, 75, 100, 125, 150, 200, 250 (depending on bore size)&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

